| --- | --- |
| **<**** 30** | **Scalping OFF, mutation OFF, trailing OFF** |
| **30–60** | **Normal mode (swing/scalp OK)** |
| **60–85** | **Mutation ON, trailing activé, TP plus large** |
| **>**** 85** | **Entrée instantanée, SL virtuel, presets boostés** |

