| **41–65** | **🟡 Tension légère** | **SL virtuel, grille OFF, ghost-only partiel** |
| **66–85** | **🔶 Stress latent** | **SignalScore +10, mutation OFF, trailing OFF** |
| **>**** 85** | **🔴 Instabilité majeure** | **Lot divisé, preset neutre, no market orders** |

