| **Module** | **Action modulée via GSS** |
| --- | --- |
| **SignalScorer** | **Boost ou rejet du score final** |
| **MutationManager** | **Activée uniquement si GSS ≥ 75** |
| **TrailingManager** | **Déclenché si GSS ≥ 70** |
| **PresetRouter** | **Charge preset “safe” si GSS ****<**** 55** |
| **RiskManager** | **Lot réduit si GSS ****<**** 65** |
| **OrderTypeSelector** | **LIMIT forcé si GSS ****<**** 60** |

