**→ Zone de compression = 9 bougies  **

**→ RSI = 61, OBV = +0.18  **

**→ Bougie cassure confirmée (range = 1.1042–1.1049)**

**🧠**** Mode scalping : breakout  **

**→ Entry = ghost STOP @ 1.1050  **

**→ TP = 9.6 pips | SL = virtuel  **

**→ Trailing delay = 1 bougie**

