**📊**** 443.4. Calcul du *****Market Directional Bias***

struct MarketBias {

   string dominantCurrency;

   string direction; // UP/DOWN

   double confidenceScore;

   string basedOn; // e.g. USDJPY + EURUSD cluster

};

Fusion des signaux sur paires majeures → Déduction :

USD STRONG → EURUSD SELL, GBPUSD SELL, USDJPY BUY

JPY STRONG → USDJPY SELL, GBPJPY SELL

AUD WEAK → AUDUSD SELL, AUDJPY SELL

**🧠**** 443.5. Application locale du biais macro**

if (MarketBias.dominantCurrency == "USD" && Symbol() == "EURUSD") {

   if (MarketBias.direction == "UP") fusion.SignalScore += 6; // biais SELL EURUSD

   if (MarketBias.direction == "DOWN") fusion.SignalScore -= 5;

}

