| Range_Mode | 42.1 | TREND_UP | Incohérent | ❌ ignoré |
| Meta_SR | 78.5 | TRANSITION | OK | 🟡 possible |
| Safe_PostNews | 66.2 | STABLE | NA | 🟠 prudence |

**⚙****️**** 473.3. Paramètres**

input bool EnableStrategyPreview = true;

input double MinStrategyScoreToRecommend = 70.0;

input bool ShowStrategyReasoningInDashboard = true;

**🧠**** 473.4. Fonction de classement**

void UpdateStrategyPreview() {

   for each strategy {

      double score = CalculateStrategyContextScore(strategy);

      StrategyPreviewTable.add(strategy, score, justification);

   }

}

