Fichier : /Files/IA/MicroSignalTracker.json

{

  "symbol": "EURUSD",

  "last_impulse": {

    "time": "2025-05-11 12:47",

    "type": "3bar up",

    "strength": 81.4,

    "score_boost": 5.0

  }

}

**⚙****️**** 485.3. Paramètres**

input bool EnableMicroImpulseDetection = true;

input int MicroSignalLookbackBars = 3;

input double MinImpulseStrengthToBoost = 75.0;

input bool RequireMicroImpulseToEnter = false;

**🧮**** 485.4. Calcul de force impulsive**

double impulseScore = (

  NumConsecutiveSameDirectionBars × 20 +

  IntraBarRangeRatio × 30 +

  ATRDelta × 50

);

Si impulseScore > MinImpulseStrengthToBoost, un **bonus de score IA** est appliqué au signal principal.

