| CLONE-RP...  | RangePivot    | Defensive  | 1.36 | +1.0% | 🟢 Actif | 30 % |

| CLONE-BK...  | Breakout_Kumo | Aggressive | 0.88 | −0.4% | 🔴 Off   | 25 % |

Inclut : histogrammes PF/Winrate, alertes IA sur dérives, suggestions de rotation.

