| RangePivot     | TrendPullback  | 0.26 | 0.78    | 0.41     | ✅ Complémentaires |

| Breakout_Kumo  | TrendPullback  | −0.12| 0.42    | 0.66     | ⛔ Incompatibles    |

| Scalping_TK    | RangePivot     | 0.48 | 0.64    | 0.29     | 🟡 Neutres         |

