| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Mercredi | CL14 | CL17 | ⚠️ Spike | 5.1 % | 🚨 3 critères | 🔁 Plan alternatif lancé |
| Jeudi | CL03 | CL03 | Stable | 2.4 % | ✅ Conforme | ✅ Plan maintenu |

