| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Breakout_Kumo | Pullback_MA200 | 0.22 | Incompatible | Blocage |
| Range_Kijun | HA_RangeConfirm | 0.87 | Redondance utile | Fusion possible |
| TrendPullback | Momentum_ADX | 0.74 | Complémentaire | Rotation autorisée |

